Products

Learn how you can make the most of financial data

  • Transactions Typically 24 months of categorized data
  • Auth Account and routing numbers
  • Balance Real-time and historical balances
  • Identity Bank account-holder information
  • Investments Retirement, brokerage, health and education
  • Assets Point-in-time snapshots of users' finances
  • Liabilities Student loan and credit card details
  • Income Employer info and depository data
